{"tid":834511,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"新手求教買邊部相機","createTime":"2018-09-24T08:46:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-24T17:08:13.000Z","uid":137360,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"644ec12c5c765c7f479cb711ceac85e05392d6a7","tid":834511,"uid":137360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T08:46:26.000Z","msg":"嚟緊十月尾會去丹麥同冰島旅行，想買部輕，影到極光，耐寒，有得反轉個mon自拍嘅相機影相+拍片，budget 4000-10000，有咩相機有得諗？<br />\n真 新手，連乜係光圈嗰時都唔識 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中秋節快樂各位清們，唔該晒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd90fb4f7f4c87fe763988d07f6c99bffb90ed7f","tid":834511,"uid":124616,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T08:47:10.000Z","msg":"唔好買"},{"pid":"57be0ecb5d29ed1ec8f12482ddc77855c0b0fad2","tid":834511,"uid":97727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T09:12:41.000Z","msg":"買便攝機 對比單反無反 無咁貴。就算之後唔用都無咁肉痛。再者，簡啲zoom range 大啲 e.g 28-200之類越遠越好 係旅遊唔洗好似單反果啲換鏡方便好多。有p mode 即係全自動模式，乜都唔洗較，你都可以旅途中慢慢試 唔識就用自動。真係到後面你識用，去較光圈 快門呢啲，再到構圖等等 到果時你再買貴啲都未遲。"},{"pid":"17d6dbf0f467230d7e555c0264e771513743a7b2","tid":834511,"uid":137360,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T09:17:57.000Z","msg":"Btw 其實xs夠唔夠打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6a9c233bc604971a6f97331ce676fc03fc05263","tid":834511,"uid":137360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd90fb4f7f4c87fe763988d07f6c99bffb90ed7f","tid":834511,"uid":124616,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T08:47:10.000Z","msg":"唔好買"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T09:18:17.000Z","msg":"Why <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92486f1d371c299ffe67f0c8dcfe6d89fbd6a324","tid":834511,"uid":28052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T10:08:13.000Z","msg":"巴打你租好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n靜